msgstr "研究と正式なバックテストの境界 (続きを読む)"

#: ../../source/api/HistoryPanel.rst:218
msgid ""
"``HistoryPanel`` 上的 ``cum_return``、``portfolio``、``plot`` 等面向**探索与粗验**；正式回测 "
"（交割、费用、信号类型、防未来函数的数据窗口等）仍由 ``Strategy`` / ``Operator`` / Backtester "
"负责。推荐读者在阅读本 API 页的同时，结合："
msgstr ""
"``HistoryPanel``, ``cum_return``, ``portfolio``, ``plot``, etc. are geared "
"toward **exploration and quick checks**; formal backtesting (settlement, "
"fees, signal types, data windows that avoid look-ahead functions, etc.) is "
"still handled by ``Strategy`` / ``Operator`` / Backtester で。読者は、この API "
"ページと合わせて読むことをお勧めします。"

